(37, 0, 'page', 0, 'franchajzing', 0, 'Франчайзинг', '', NULL, '<div class=\\"moduleBox\\">\r\n<div class=\\"content\\">\r\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h1>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center;\\" class=\\"MsoNormal\\"><b><span style=\\"font-size:20.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nRU\\">Откройте фирменный магазин &laquo;Дом бусин&raquo; в своем городе!<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n</h1>\r\n<h3><b><span style=\\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nRU\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3>\r\n<h3><img width=\\"750\\" height=\\"296\\" alt=\\"\\" src=\\"/pic/фасад  Москва 2 - копия копия1(1).jpg\\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Verdana;\\">\r\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\\" class=\\"MsoNormal\\"><b><span style=\\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nRU\\">Франшиза компании &laquo;Дом бусин&raquo;</span></b><span style=\\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:RU\\">&nbsp;&mdash; это великолепное сочетание простого в управлении формата магазина по продаже бусин и фурнитуры для бижутерии&nbsp; и высокорентабельного бизнеса.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\\" class=\\"MsoNormal\\"><span style=\\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:RU\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\\" class=\\"MsoNormal\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\\" class=\\"MsoNormal\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\\" class=\\"MsoNormal\\"><span style=\\"font-family: Verdana;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">Для партнера по франчайзингу мы разработали оптимальный пакет сотрудничества, реализация которого позволяет сделать бизнес нашего партнера максимально эффективным.</span></span><span style=\\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nRU\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\\"font-family: Verdana;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 12pt;\\">&nbsp;</span></span></h3>\r\n<h3>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\\" class=\\"MsoNormal\\"><b><span style=\\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nRU\\"><img width=\\"200\\" height=\\"200\\" align=\\"absMiddle\\" alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://s020.radikal.ru/i718/1311/18/9f8bf4258440.jpg\\" />&nbsp; &nbsp;Наши преимущества:</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;\\" class=\\"MsoNormal\\"><b><span style=\\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso